maged Items in Transport If there is any damage to the packaging on delivery, contact us immediately at Sparkluslamps@gmail.com or call us at 9548218100.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Questions If you have any questions about the delivery and shipment of your order, please contact us at Sparkluslamps@gmail.com or call us at 9548218100.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Faster Delivery or Bulk Orders For faster delivery or bulk orders, please get in touch with us directly at Sparkluslamps@gmail.com or call us at 9548218100. We’re happy to discuss your specific needs and work out a solution that suits you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please note that our shipping operations are handled by a third-party logistics provider. This helps us ensure that your order is delivered in a timely and efficient manner.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Shipping Policy','','publish','closed','closed','','shipping-policy','','','2024-07-08 02:51:47','2024-07-07 21:21:47','',0,'https://sparkluslamps.com/?page_id=633',0,'page','',0);
